description.value: A subset of the Snomed-CT clinical terminology (i.e. coding system) intended for use in the UK, previously named SnomedCTUK, that describes the type of service provided or requested to the patient. Any code from the SNOMED CT UK CDA Care Setting Type subset with subset original id 1071000000135.
